Class PartialBuffer

java.lang.Object
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.actor.Behavior
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.examples.buffer.Buffer
it.unipr.sowide.actodes.examples.buffer.PartialBuffer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public final class PartialBuffer
extends Buffer
The PartialBuffer class defines a behavior that manages a buffer with a partial occupation. This behavior can move to either the EmptyBuffer or the FullBuffer behavior.
See Also:
EmptyBuffer, FullBuffer, Serialized Form
